      • getSourceAbiVerificationMode

        public JavaBuckConfig.SourceAbiVerificationMode getSourceAbiVerificationMode()
        Controls a special verification mode that generates ABIs both from source and from class files and diffs them. This is a test hook for use during development of the source ABI feature. This only has meaning when getAbiGenerationMode() is one of the source modes.
